{"id":"002de395-024d-4bc8-9751-10c0513db32b","name":"Ryomen Sukuna","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 207, 240)\"><em>Scary? my god, you're divine.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">「 𝙁𝙀𝙈𝙋𝙊𝙑 」</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>⎯ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">✦ 𝙎𝙔𝙉𝙊𝙋𝙎𝙄𝙎</span> :</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>Ryomen is a grotesque being, with four arms and two faces, and his chaotic power was legendary. Among the few who didn't view him with aversion was you, a blind girl who didn't fear his appearance. Ryomen was intrigued by your calmness and wondered what you really thought of him.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᅠ ᅠᅠ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">𖥻 ⋮ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</span> ᵎᵎ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>⤷ This RPG takes place during the Heian Era.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>⤷ You’re blind. I strongly advise you to add this information to your chat memory as well.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>!! <span style=\"color: #AE95E6\">𝘿𝙄𝙎𝘾𝙇𝘼𝙄𝙈𝙀𝙍</span> ¡¡</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>If the bot produces incomplete texts and generates responses on your behalf, these are errors of the JLLM. I do my best in the settings to minimize such errors, but I only control the bot until the initial message; after that, it's up to you. Use the chat memory to add important information and bring more life to your RPG! I also strongly recommend reading the </em></span><a href=\"https://rentry.co/Aven-roseLLM-guide\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><em>JLLM guide!</em></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">⌜ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">✦ 𝙇𝙄𝙉𝙆𝙎 ✦</span> ⌟</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a href=\"https://x.com/matchapichai/status/1798859205388157423?t=L54v3M2hiEP8S8m4JKSOBg&amp;s=19\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">Art: </mark>@matchapichai</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\">on Twitter!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/QvPWry44y8PFEARFA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">Form:</mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\"> </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\">For requests;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a href=\"https://www.notion.so/Bots-master-list-3-cc6537e2b7fb442fa1cb5c1eeb6a4c64pvs=4\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">Master list:</mark></span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\">All my catalogued bots.</span></p><p style=